# RNA feature 3D residue labels.
# Labels are created as independent grouped models under #348.2.
# Fetch and run the self-contained RNA label script from GitHub.
open https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mvorlander/spliceosome-structure-vis/main/scripts/label_scripts/6qx9_rna_labels.py
view
show nucleic
